summary: I have some tickets to Dan and Phil’s Interactive Introverts that I’m looking to quickly resell or potentially give away. We...
body:
I have some tickets to Dan and Phil’s Interactive Introverts that I’m looking to quickly resell or potentially give away. We ended up accidentally purchasing more tickets than we needed. The show is at Fox Theater in Detroit Michigan.

3 tickets in total. 

Two of them are really good seats very close to the stage (we paid $79.00) and the other is further back, but still quite good (paid $34.00).

Message me for more information. I’m still going to this show. So, we can meet up there if you’d like to grab the tickets in person. :)

blog.title: I Hope Your Day Is Good
blog.description:
I post a lot of random shit like honestly I’m so sorry

Photo Credit: me

body:
Interactive introverts spoilers ahead

Omg the show was amazing I had so much fun and couldn’t stop laughing. By the end of the show my cheeks actually hurt from laughing so much.

Some highlights

- the pre show playlist was the best fuckin thing

- everyone dancing/ cheering on the people who were

- the pickle festival jokes

- the Yee

- the person on the top tier that was dancing omg you were great

- the people on the left tier thing that started the Macarena

- Welcome to the Black Parade playing right before the show

- the lights were amazing, epilepsy warning btw

- “things we will defiantly not do on stage” while they do them

- Phil’s rap omg

- dan playing the piano without sheet music

- the audience being respectful, this was the first show of theirs I saw and I was a little worried about that

- the jokes at their old branding

- the jokes at Phan

- the overall vibe of the show

- how everything flowed into the next thing

- The wheel I was low key concerned but I worry about everything

- “lady door was an inside job”

- we killed dan like come on guys

- “who are dan and phil?” 16%

- the awards at the end

- I got to go with my friend

- the amazing people at the merch stand that line didn’t ever stop moving for more then 3 mins


omg there’s so much more I’ll probably add to this but I had such an amazing time

summary:
7/20/18💞

 @danielhowell @amazingphil I was so in shock that I could hardly say anything, but I wish I had said that I love you...
caption:
7/20/18💞


@danielhowell @amazingphil I was so in shock that I could hardly say anything, but I wish I had said that I love you and you mean the world to me, that you’ve helped me through everything and you were always there when nobody else was. I’m so sorry I didn’t tell you but I hope you know that I love you so so much and I will never forget what you guys have done for me. Thank you for an amazing performance that made me have so so so much fun and helping me make new friends online that I was able to meet at this show!! You guys are honestly the nicest people I have ever met. This whole experience blew me away. I was on the edge of my seat laughing, crying and screaming all at the same time! I love you and I hope you’ll come back to visit someday!☺️❤️
